{"article_id":"CwShFURfYjCaLuOX","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"U.S. Secretary of State Mike Pompeo wrapped up his fourth visit to North Korea on Sunday ,","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"describing his talks with leader Kim Jong Un as productive .","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"Pompeo met with Kim for about two hours ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"according to a pool report from CBS ' Kylie Atwood , the only U.S. journalist","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"who accompanied the secretary on his trip .","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"The visit comes after President Trump 's historic summit with Kim in June ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"which resulted in a vague commitment from Pyongyang","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"to denuclearize .","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"`` Had a good trip to # Pyongyang","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"to meet with Chairman Kim , ''","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"Pompeo said on Twitter ,","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"adding","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"that the leaders `` continue to make progress on agreements","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"made at Singapore Summit . ''","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"A U.S. official","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"who accompanied Pompeo on the trip ,","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"and spoke to Fox News on the condition of anonymity ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"the Sunday meeting was `` better than the last time ''","depth":7},{"id":19,"text":"but that `` it 's going to be a long haul . ''","depth":7},{"id":20,"text":"After their private meeting , Kim hosted Pompeo for lunch at the Paekhwawon State Guest House .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"As Pompeo waited for him ,","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"he clasped his hands in front of his body","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"and State Department spokesperson Heather Nauert said ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"`` It 's like you are standing at the alt [ a ] r , ''","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"according to the pool report .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"Pompeo smiled","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"but said nothing in return .","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"`` So is everything OK ? ''","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"Kim asked through an interpreter","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"as they walked toward the banquet hall .","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"`` Everything is great , ''","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"Pompeo said .","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"`` Everything is great .","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"I am very much looking forward to our time together too . ''","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"As the guests took their seats at the table ,","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"Kim said ,","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"`` It 's a very nice day","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"that promises a good future for both countries . ''","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Pompeo thanked him","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"for hosting the event","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"and conveyed President Trump 's regards .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Later that afternoon , Pompeo touched down in Seoul","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"to meet with South Korean President Moon Jae-in .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"Moon thanked Pompeo","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"for coming straight to the capital after his meeting with Kim ,","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"calling it a very important day .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"He said ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"`` I dearly hope","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"that your latest visit , as well as the upcoming U.S.-North Korea summit ,","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"which","depth":15},{"id":51,"text":"I hope","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"will be happening soon ,","depth":14},{"id":53,"text":"will make an irreversible and decisive progress in terms of complete denuclearization on the Korean Peninsula as well as the peace process . ''","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"He asked Pompeo to share what he could with the public .","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"Pompeo thanked him","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"and said ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"`` I do n't have much to add .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"I will certainly tell you in private about our conversation ,","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"but we had a good , productive conversation . ''","depth":13},{"id":60,"text":"He continued ,","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"`` As President Trump has said ,","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"there are many steps along the way","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"and we took one of those today ;","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"it was another step forward . ''","depth":11},{"id":65,"text":"Pompeo offered no further details ,","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"such as whether he had established a time and place for a second summit","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"or what either side was demanding ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"but Moon 's press secretary shared more in a statement","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"reported by South Korean news agency Yonhap :","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"At a closed meeting , Pompeo told Moon","depth":13},{"id":71,"text":"that he and Kim agreed to arrange a second U.S.-North Korea summit `` at the earliest possible date , ''","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"as well as discuss the specifics of date and location ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"Press Secretary Yoon Young-chan said .","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"Pompeo also spoke about additional denuclearization steps and Washington 's monitoring of the verification process and `` corresponding measures , ''","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"Yoon said .","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"`` The two sides will form working-level negotiation teams","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"to discuss North Korea 's denuclearization process and Trump-Kim summit schedule , ''","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"Yoon said .","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"Spokesperson Heather Nauert said later on Sunday","depth":6},{"id":80,"text":"that Pompeo and Kim also agreed to instruct their working-level teams to meet soon ,","depth":7},{"id":81,"text":"and that Kim invited inspectors to visit the Punggye Ri nuclear test site","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"to confirm","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"that it had been irreversibly dismantled .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"The U.S. , in its mission for a fully verified denuclearization of North Korea , demands","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"that the country turn over a full inventory of its nuclear weapons program .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"North Korea has rejected those demands","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"and wants sanctions to be lifted","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"before nuclear talks proceed .","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"South Korea has suggested","depth":7},{"id":90,"text":"that the U.S. sign a treaty","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"formally ending the Korean War ,","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"in exchange for North Korea closing its main nuclear plant ,","depth":8},{"id":93,"text":"as NPR 's Anthony Kuhn reported for our Newscast .","depth":6},{"id":94,"text":"Gridlock has been part and parcel of the negotiation process .","depth":4},{"id":95,"text":"In August , Trump canceled Pompeo 's trip to North Korea","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"because they were `` not making sufficient progress '' in the denuclearization of the Korean Peninsula ,","depth":6},{"id":97,"text":"he said .","depth":5},{"id":98,"text":"On Sunday , after Pompeo 's meeting with Kim , Trump tweeted","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"`` Progress made on Singapore Summit Agreements !","depth":6},{"id":100,"text":"I look forward to seeing Chairman Kim again , in the near future . ''","depth":6},{"id":101,"text":"Pompeo 's trip started with a visit to Tokyo on Friday ,","depth":3},{"id":102,"text":"where he met with Japanese Prime Minister Shinzo Abe","depth":4},{"id":103,"text":"to coordinate positions in the push","depth":5},{"id":104,"text":"to get Pyongyang to relinquish its nuclear weapons .","depth":5},{"id":105,"text":"On Monday , Pompeo is expected to land in Beijing","depth":3},{"id":106,"text":"- the last stop on his whirlwind diplomatic tour .","depth":3}],"relations":[{"parent":213,"left"